#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.48"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.48:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.48:0.2"
msgid "5. Papātavagga"
msgstr "5. A Cliff"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 48. Dutiyachiggaḷayugasutta → dutiyachiggalasuttaṃ (bj) | chiggaḷa 3 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.48:0.3"
msgid "48. Dutiyachiggaḷayugasutta"
msgstr "48. A Yoke With a Hole (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.457"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.48:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ayaṃ mahāpathavī ekodakā assa."
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose the earth was entirely covered with water."

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.2"
msgid "Tatra puriso ekacchiggaḷaṃ yugaṃ pakkhipeyya."
msgstr "And a person threw a yoke with a single hole into it."

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ puratthimo vāto pacchimena saṃhareyya, pacchimo vāto puratthimena "
"saṃhareyya, uttaro vāto dakkhiṇena saṃhareyya, dakkhiṇo vāto uttarena "
"saṃhareyya."
msgstr ""
"The east wind wafts it west; the west wind wafts it east; the north wind "
"wafts it south; and the south wind wafts it north."

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.4"
msgid ""
"Tatrassa kāṇo kacchapo. So vassasatassa vassasatassa accayena sakiṃ sakiṃ "
"ummujjeyya."
msgstr "And there was a one-eyed turtle who popped up once every hundred years."

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.6"
msgid ""
"api nu kho kāṇo kacchapo vassasatassa vassasatassa accayena sakiṃ sakiṃ "
"ummujjanto amusmiṃ ekacchiggaḷe yuge gīvaṃ paveseyyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Would that one-eyed turtle, popping up once every hundred years, still poke "
"its neck through the hole in that yoke?”"

# Reading adhicca as “chance” (BB) or “coincidence” (Thanissaro) here are untenable.
msgctxt "sn56.48:1.7"
msgid ""
"“Adhiccamidaṃ, bhante, yaṃ so kāṇo kacchapo vassasatassa vassasatassa "
"accayena sakiṃ sakiṃ ummujjanto amusmiṃ ekacchiggaḷe yuge gīvaṃ paveseyyā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s unlikely, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.48:2.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ adhiccamidaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ manussattaṃ labhati."
msgstr "“That’s how unlikely it is to get reborn as a human being."

msgctxt "sn56.48:2.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ adhiccamidaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ "
"sammāsambuddho."
msgstr ""
"And that’s how unlikely it is for a Realized One to arise in the world, a "
"perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha."

msgctxt "sn56.48:2.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ adhiccamidaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ tathāgatappavedito dhammavinayo loke "
"dibbati."
msgstr ""
"And that’s how unlikely it is for the teaching and training proclaimed by a "
"Realized One to shine in the world."

#. VAR: Tassidaṃ → tayidaṃ (?)
msgctxt "sn56.48:2.4"
msgid ""
"Tassidaṃ, bhikkhave, manussattaṃ laddhaṃ, tathāgato loke uppanno arahaṃ "
"sammāsambuddho, tathāgatappavedito ca dhammavinayo loke dibbati."
msgstr ""
"And now, mendicants, you have been reborn as a human being. A Realized One "
"has arisen in the world, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha. And the "
"teaching and training proclaimed by a Realized One shines in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.48:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.48:3.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
